briefdescription.para: Mapping from AxisGroup to list of fields bound to that group.
add the axis field to the list specified by axisGroup

detaileddescription.para: The map is built from all KSPAxisField tagged float fields in all part modules on all parts of the vessel.

briefdescription.para: Increment the values of all axis fields in the group.

detaileddescription.para: The field values will be incremented by their respective speeds scaled by axisRate. Negative axisRate means the field values will be decremented.

briefdescription.para: Update the values of all axis fields in the group according to their modes.
